{
  "1804010": {
    "name": "魔王的迷宫",
    "steam_appid": 1804010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804010/extras/e3de06dbc4ef3bc0768939645d39e091.poster.avif?t=1747148410\" width=600 height=454 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804010/extras/e3de06dbc4ef3bc0768939645d39e091.webm?t=1747148410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804010/extras/e3de06dbc4ef3bc0768939645d39e091.mp4?t=1747148410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《魔王的迷宫》是一款具有挑战性的第一人称地下城探索游戏，背景设定在受恶魔侵袭的神话般的封建日本。</strong>作为一名孤军奋战的步卒，踏上征途追寻并杀死杀害你主公的魔王。但是，你是否有足够的技巧、资源和毅力，在这残酷的世界中生存下来，并战胜即将到来的所有恐怖？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“世界陷入混乱，进入了末法时代。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>社会分崩离析，战火蔓延全国。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>瘟疫和饥荒夺走成千上万条生命，恶魔在这片土地上肆虐。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你将扮演一名‘足轻’，效忠于武田信光大人的步卒。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你的主公被一个强大的魔王所欺骗，带领军队陷入了埋伏。除你之外，其余人全部阵亡。你的主公没有听从你的意愿，选择了牺牲自己以帮助你逃离战场。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你发誓要找到那个背叛你主公的恶魔，并结束它的生命。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你深吸一口可能是你在凡间的最后一口气，义无反顾地准备进入…</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>魔王的迷宫！”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>游戏特色：</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804010/extras/e7ca92d9e1dd65a0562779a138131505.poster.avif?t=1747148410\" width=600 height=454 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804010/extras/e7ca92d9e1dd65a0562779a138131505.webm?t=1747148410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804010/extras/e7ca92d9e1dd65a0562779a138131505.mp4?t=1747148410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索阴森世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于魔王那令人不安的黑暗世界。这一设定灵感源自封建日本，以精美的复古阴森艺术风格呈现，配以抖动滤镜，带来纯正的 PS1 时代质感。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在战斗中证明自己</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你的智慧和一系列精选的武器武装自己，从武士刀和薙刀到火枪和弓箭，参与残酷而富有挑战性的战斗。击败来自日本古代神话的各种妖怪以及潜伏在迷宫中的其他恐怖怪物，尽情享受成就感和极度满足感。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索迷宫</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在迷宫黑暗扭曲的走廊中艰难前行，探索每一个角落以寻找有限的资源。盔甲套装和护身符能改变战斗运势，重要线索则可以帮助你解开魔王布下的谜题。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>抉择，是敌是友？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中与其他奇怪的角色互动。有些能提供你所需之物，有些则能让你得到片刻喘息，但要小心选择信任对象，这可能会影响你的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804010/extras/3622884e18f7accf0c4b4dcbd7eb984b.poster.avif?t=1747148410\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804010/extras/3622884e18f7accf0c4b4dcbd7eb984b.webm?t=1747148410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804010/extras/3622884e18f7accf0c4b4dcbd7eb984b.mp4?t=1747148410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
